18. Nc3 - After dealing with the Wicked Witch I now consolidate and develop my second knight.  After black's next move, however, 18....... Ke5 I land a coup de grace with my horsie jumping on to c7.  The rook on a8 is toast and Scalawag waves that white flag!  I am now about to go away on holiday to sunny Cornwall for two weeks, returning on 28th August!  I will be back to annotate more games then but it is cheers and bye for now from me, Joanne.
